				<td colspan="2"><span>The problem with people getting to 40 in a week part-time is that people dont learn much in that time period. This leads to bad player. This leads to sucky groups, which leads to much death. Much deathleads to people quitting EQ, which leaves servers with a higher ratio of incompetent morons to skilled players.
<br />

<br />
But thats besides the point. Chant is a term I hear on a daily basis. Theres just some things you can't avoid. I worry when people reach upper levels and ask quetions that shouldn't be asked. Come on, even if you did get 40 in a week, it doesn't take a brain surgeon to figure out what 'chant' stands for.
<br />

<br />
