Anyhow,to answer, take a look at your song line-up. All those songs you have with the word &quot;chant&quot; in them are used for chant kiting. AFAIK it is not kiting in the typical sense, more just doing direct damage to a mob by way of song. Take a look at the guides to the left of the posts. That's what I've been able to get between the lines of the discussions here.
<br />

<br />
You can still swarm, or so I'm told<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> Personally I die atm(Any bards on The Seventh Hammer willing to meet for an hour's hard lesson?). But, using a pet, take a whole pocket of mobs, let them beat your pet almost to death then kill your pet yourself for the XP. Again the guides to the left can help with details.
<br />

